trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormat"></xref> objects within a control designer.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en samling av <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormat"> </xref> objekter i en kontroll designer.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> class and any derived class defines the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.AutoFormats%2A> property as a DesignerAutoFormatCollection object.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>klassen og alle utledede klassen definerer den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.AutoFormats%2A>egenskapen som et DesignerAutoFormatCollection-objekt.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.AutoFormats%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Control developers can override the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.AutoFormats%2A> property in a derived control designer, add custom automatic formatting styles, and return the collection of supported formats to the visual designer.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollutviklere kan overstyre den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.AutoFormats%2A>egenskap i en avledet kontrollen utformer Legg til egendefinert automatiske formatering stiler og returnere samlingen over formater som støttes til den visuelle utformeren.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.AutoFormats%2A>

trans-unit.source: The collection dynamically increases as objects are added.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen øker dynamisk som legges til objektene.

trans-unit.source: Indexes in this collection are zero-based.
trans-unit.target: Indekser i denne samlingen er null.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Count%2A> property to determine how many automatic style formats are in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Count%2A>til å fastslå hvor mange automatisk stilen formater er i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Count%2A>

trans-unit.source: Additionally, use the DesignerAutoFormatCollection methods and properties to provide the following functionality: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Add%2A> method to add a single format to the collection.
trans-unit.target: I tillegg bruke DesignerAutoFormatCollection metodene og egenskapene til å gi følgende funksjonalitet: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Add%2A>metode for å legge til en enkelt format i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Add%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Insert%2A> method to add a format at a particular index within the collection.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Insert%2A>Metode for å legge til et format på en bestemt indeks i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Insert%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Remove%2A> method to remove a format.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Remove%2A>Metode for å fjerne en formatet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Remove%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.RemoveAt%2A> method to remove the format at a particular index.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.RemoveAt%2A>Metode for å fjerne formatet på en bestemt indeks.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.RemoveAt%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Contains%2A> method to determine whether a particular format is already in the collection.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Contains%2A>Metode for å finne ut om et bestemt format er allerede i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Contains%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.IndexOf%2A> method to retrieve the index of a format within the collection.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.IndexOf%2A>Metode for å hente indeksen for et format i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.IndexOf%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Item%2A> property to get or set the format at a particular index, using array notation.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Item%2A>Til å hente eller angi på en bestemt indeks ved hjelp av matrise notasjon.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Item%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Clear%2A> method to remove all formats from the collection.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Clear%2A>Metode for å fjerne alle formater fra samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Clear%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Count%2A> property to determine the number of formats in the collection.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Count%2A>Til å fastslå hvor mange formater i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Count%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.IndexOf%2A> method to get the position of a format within the collection.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.IndexOf%2A>Metode for å få plasseringen format i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.IndexOf%2A>

trans-unit.target: Henter antall <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormat"> </xref> objekter i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The Count property typically is used to determine the upper boundary index when iterating through objects in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Count-egenskapen brukes vanligvis til å bestemme den øvre grense på nytt når gjentakelse objekter i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Because the collection indexes are zero-based, the first element is at index `0` and the last element is at index `Count-1`.
trans-unit.target: Fordi samlingen indeksene nullbasert, er det første elementet i indeksen `0` , og det siste elementet i indeksen `Count-1`.

trans-unit.target: Antall <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormat"> </xref> objekter i samlingen.

trans-unit.target: Returnerer indeksen for den angitte <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormat"> </xref> objekt i samlingen.

trans-unit.target: Den nullbaserte indeksen for den første forekomsten av format i samlingen; ellers, -1, hvis formatet ikke er i samlingen.

trans-unit.target: Setter inn en <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormat"> </xref> objektet i samlingen i den angitte indeksen.

trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Når du setter inn et element i en samling, indeksverdiene endres for etterfølgende elementer i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index within the collection at which to insert `format`.
trans-unit.target: Den nullbaserte indeksen i samlingen som skal settes inn `format`.

trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormat"> </xref> objektet i den angitte indeksen i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Use the Item indexer to retrieve the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormat> object at the specified index within the collection or to set the format at the specified index within the collection.
trans-unit.target: Bruk elementet indekserer til å hente den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormat>objektet i den angitte indeksen i samlingen, eller til å angi formatet i den angitte indeksen i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormat>

trans-unit.source: You can index elements in the collection by using array notation.
trans-unit.target: Du kan indeksere elementer i samlingen ved hjelp av matrise notasjon.

trans-unit.source: For example, you can index an element at index `i` with the notation `AutoFormats(i)` for Microsoft VisualBasic or `AutoFormats[i]` for C#.
trans-unit.target: Du kan for eksempel indeksere en elementet i indeksen `i` med notasjonen `AutoFormats(i)` for Microsoft VisualBasic eller `AutoFormats[i]` for C#.

trans-unit.source: When you have a reference to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormat> object and need the index of the object in the collection, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.IndexOf%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Når du har en referanse til det <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormat>objekt og må indeksen for objektet i samlingen, bruker den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.IndexOf%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.IndexOf%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormat>

trans-unit.source: Gets the maximum outer dimensions of the control as it will appear at run time.
trans-unit.target: Henter de maksimale ytre dimensjonene kontrollens som vises på kjøretidspunktet.

trans-unit.source: The PreviewSize property examines each format in the collection and returns the largest height and the largest width in a <xref:System.Drawing.Size> structure.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen PreviewSize undersøker hvert format i samlingen, og returnerer den største høyden og bredden største i en <xref:System.Drawing.Size>strukturen.</xref:System.Drawing.Size>

trans-unit.source: A visual designer, such as [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], uses the PreviewSize to determine the initial size of the **AutoFormat** dialog box.
trans-unit.target: En visuell effekt designer som [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], bruker du PreviewSize til å bestemme den opprinnelige størrelsen på den **fortløpende** dialogboksen.

trans-unit.source: The minimum size is 200-by-200 pixels.
trans-unit.target: Minimumsstørrelsen er 200 ved 200 piksler.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Size"></xref> structure that contains the height and width of the control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Size"> </xref> struktur som inneholder høyden og bredden på kontrollen i utformingsoverflaten.

trans-unit.source: Removes the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormat"></xref> object from the collection.
trans-unit.target: Fjerner det angitte <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormat"> </xref> objektet fra samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The Remove method removes the first occurrence of `format` from the collection.
trans-unit.target: Remove-metoden fjerner den første forekomsten av `format` fra samlingen.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection> object does not contain `format`, the collection remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection>objektet inneholder ikke `format`, samlingen forblir uendret.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection>

trans-unit.source: No exception is thrown.
trans-unit.target: Ingen unntak.

trans-unit.source: The Remove method determines equality by using the <xref:System.Object.Equals%2A> method on the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormat> objects that are being compared.
trans-unit.target: Remove-metoden bestemmer likhet ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Object.Equals%2A>-metoden på den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormat>objekter som sammenlignes.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormat> </xref:System.Object.Equals%2A>

trans-unit.source: The Remove method performs a linear search; therefore, the average execution time is proportional to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Count%2A> value.
trans-unit.target: Remove-metoden utfører en lineær søket. Gjennomsnittlig kjøringstid er derfor proporsjonalt den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Count%2A>verdi.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Count%2A>

trans-unit.source: To remove a format at a particular index from the collection, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.RemoveAt%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil fjerne en formatet i en bestemt indeks fra samlingen, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.RemoveAt%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.RemoveAt%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets an object that can be used to synchronize access to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter et objekt som kan brukes til å synkronisere tilgang til den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Enumerating through a collection is not a thread-safe procedure intrinsically.
trans-unit.target: Lister opp i en samling er ikke en sikker prosedyre gjelder.

trans-unit.source: Even when a collection is synchronized, other threads can still modify the collection.
trans-unit.target: Selv når en samling synkroniseres, kan andre tråder fortsatt endre samlingen.

trans-unit.source: This causes exceptions during enumeration.
trans-unit.target: Dette gjør unntak under opplisting.

trans-unit.source: Lock the collection by using the SyncRoot method during the entire enumeration to guarantee thread safety.
trans-unit.target: Lås samlingen ved hjelp av metoden SyncRoot under hele opplistingen garantere tråd sikkerhet.

trans-unit.source: For detailed information about locking collections for thread-safe access, see <xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Detaljert informasjon om låsetillatelse samlinger for sikker tilgang, kan du se <xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: An object that can be used to synchronize access to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection"></xref>.
